description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which features a BBQ at Kyle's and some monologuing from Aaron. On Real Housewives of New York, the women have one last dinner in Newport and a sober tea party.


RHOBH Recap: Beginning

RHONY Recap: 27:35ish
